Question: Is the pot to the left or to the right of the pan?

Reference Answer: left

Image path: ./sampled_GQA/n184385.jpg

Program:

```
BOX0=LOC(image=IMAGE,object='pan')
IMAGE0=CROP(image=IMAGE,box=BOX0)
BOX1=LOC(image=IMAGE0,object='pot')
ANSWER0=COUNT(box=BOX1)
ANSWER1=EVAL(expr="'left' if {ANSWER0} > 0 else 'right'")
FINAL_RESULT=RESULT(var=ANSWER1)
```
